* Nor do the wind,
the sun or the rain *

1:46:10.620 --> 1:46:12.706
* We can be like they are *

1:46:12.747 --> 1:46:14.332
* Come on, baby *

1:46:14.374 --> 1:46:15.834
* Don't fear the reaper *

