* Take my heart *

1:47:23.943 --> 1:47:26.821
* And burn it down *

1:47:33.244 --> 1:47:35.497
* *

1:48:00.230 --> 1:48:02.315
* We were young *

1:48:02.357 --> 1:48:05.902
* And I was broken *

1:48:09.364 --> 1:48:11.616
* You tried to run *

1:48:11.658 --> 1:48:15.245
* But I'm an ocean *

1:48:18.915 --> 1:48:20.875
* When it's done *

1:48:20.917 --> 1:48:24.879
* It drags us both in *

1:48:28.341 --> 1:48:30.510
* 'Cause I was young *

1:48:30.552 --> 1:48:34.264
* And I was broken. *

1:48:48.278 --> 1:48:50.030
(song ends)

1:48:50.071 --> 1:48:53.033
